==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Minute-jack
<hw>Mi*nute"-jack`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
figure which strikes the hour on the bell of some fanciful clocks; --
called also <altname>jack of the clock house</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A timeserver; an inconstant person.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Minutely</ent>⟦br⟧
